Casino awards Jonás Larrazábal, who comes free
After 72 days of silence, Casino Red's agent freed the mayor of Monterrey's brother from the trial that was being waged against him for alleged extortion.
After 72 days of imprisonment, Manuel Jonás Larrazábal is released after the agent of Casino Red has given him the trial of the brother of the mayor of Monterrey for extortion before the district's Second Criminal Court.
