The Institute of Science and International Security ISIS is based on the recent report of the International Agency for Nuclear Safety AIEA and other documents originating from this UN agency to investigate this scientist.
OIOs last week shared their "serious concern" about a "possible military dimension" of Iran's nuclear programme.
